#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Z-1 Assault is a balanced and 'powerful' assault rifle suitable for short and medium range engagements produced by <info>Z-Arm Tech</info>.\n"
"the Z-1 Assault uses <info>small caliber</info> ammunition, it is modeled after the M4 (most likely the Colt Commando variation) with a futuristic design. It has the word 'Z-1' right in front of its trigger. It has scratches and some duct tape wrapped over its stock, carry handle, grip and handguard, which proves this gun has been well used and is now in bad condition but still somewhat usable.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <bad>poorly made</bad> and will <bad>easily malfunction</bad> and will <bad>not handle much if any beating</bad>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"Z-1突击步枪是由<info>Z-Arm科技</info>生产的一款平衡且“威力强大”的突击步枪，适用于中近距离交战。\n"
"Z-1突击步枪使用<info>小口径</info>弹药，其设计以M4（很可能是Colt Commando变体）为蓝本，融合了未来主义风格。扳机正前方刻有“Z-1”字样。枪托、提把、握把和护木上布满划痕并缠有胶带，证明此枪已被频繁使用，目前状态不佳但仍勉强可用。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<bad>做工粗糙</bad>，<bad>容易发生故障</bad>，且<bad>无法承受过多磕碰</bad>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

