msgid_plural "Z-2 LMPs"
msgstr[0] "Z-2 LMP"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Z-2 LMP is a <info>small caliber</info> SMG ideal for fast movement and maneuverability produced by <info>Z-Arm Tech</info>\n"
"Z-2 LMP resembles a MP5 without the adjustable stock, the rear sight, has a reflex sight and a vertical foregrip. It has the word 'Z-2' right in front of its selective-fire switch. It has scratches & some duct tapes wrapped over its grip, which means this gun is now under bad condition but still usable.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <bad>poorly made</bad> and will <bad>easily malfunction</bad> and will <bad>not handle much if any beating</bad>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"Z-2 LMP是一款由<info>Z-Arm Tech</info>生产的<info>小口径</info>冲锋枪，非常适合快速移动和机动。\n"
"Z-2 LMP类似于没有可调枪托和后瞄准具的MP5，配有反射式瞄准镜和垂直前握把。其快慢机开关正前方刻有“Z-2”字样。枪身有划痕，握把处缠着一些胶带，这意味着这把枪目前状况不佳但仍可使用。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<bad>做工粗糙</bad>，<bad>容易发生故障</bad>，并且<bad>经不起多少磕碰</bad>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
