"\n"
"This weapon is <good>reinforced</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"Z-1 突击是一款由<info>Z-Arm Tech</info>生产的平衡且“强力”的突击步枪，适合中近距离交战。\n"
