#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "HVM Advertisement paper"
msgid_plural "HVM Advertisement papers"
msgstr[0] "HVM 广告传单"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'HVM Advertisement paper', 'str_pl': 'HVM
#. Advertisement papers'}
#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"'High Value Metrics is proud to present it's latest HVM weapons line!' \n"
"a broad number of images of weapons are placed across the flier, \n"
"a picture of a pistol named HVM 001, \n"
"a frail looking SMG named HVM 002, \n"
"a sturdy but clunky assault rifle named HVM 005 G-Class, \n"
"a very heavy looking LMG called HVM 008, \n"
"and a shotgun across the background with 'HVM 004, where nanomaterials make the impossible come reality' written under it as 25 shotgun shells are placed under it, \n"
"all weapons have green and light brown digital pattern camo panels ontop of very dark gray internals.\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"“高价值指标公司自豪地推出其最新的HVM武器系列！”\n"
"传单上印有大量武器图片，\n"
"包括一把名为HVM 001的手枪，\n"
"一把看起来脆弱的冲锋枪HVM 002，\n"
"一把坚固但笨重的突击步枪HVM 005 G-Class，\n"
"一把看起来非常沉重的轻机枪HVM 008，\n"
"以及背景中的一把霰弹枪，下方写着“HVM 004，纳米材料让不可能成为现实”，并配有25发霰弹枪子弹，\n"
"所有武器都在深灰色内部结构上覆盖着绿色和浅棕色数字迷彩面板。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "HVM 001"
msgid_plural "HVM 001"
msgstr[0] "HVM 001"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the HVM 001 is the first gun manufactured by <info>High Value Metrics (HVM)</info> \n"
"it is the weakest gun in the line of weapons produced by this company. \n"
"it uses a <info>small caliber</info> ammunition type, and looks like a futuristic Glock-shaped pistol that features its magazine placed under the barrel similar to the Mauser C96 with a stylish green camo pattern.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>average</color> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"HVM 001 是 <info>高价值指标公司（HVM）</info> 制造的第一款枪械。\n"
"它是该公司生产的武器系列中最弱的一款。\n"
"它使用 <info>小口径</info> 弹药，外形类似一把未来风格的格洛克式手枪，其弹匣置于枪管下方，类似于毛瑟 C96，并带有时尚的绿色迷彩涂装。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <color_yellow>中等</color>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "HVM 002"
msgid_plural "HVM 002"
msgstr[0] "HVM 002"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the HVM 002 is the second gun manufactured by <info>High Value Metrics (HVM)</info> \n"
"it's the weakest SMG in the line of weapons produced by this company. \n"
"it uses the same <info>small caliber</info> ammunition as the HVM 001, and is a bullpup SMG possibly modeled after an Uzi or an MP7 with a fixed stock, a vertical foregrip and an unused top rail with a stylish green camo pattern.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>average</color> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"HVM 002 是 <info>高价值指标公司（HVM）</info> 制造的第二款枪械。\n"
"它是该公司生产的武器系列中最弱的冲锋枪。\n"
"它使用与 HVM 001 相同的 <info>小口径</info> 弹药，是一款无托式冲锋枪，可能以乌兹或 MP7 为原型，配有固定枪托、垂直前握把、未使用的顶部导轨以及时尚的绿色迷彩涂装。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <color_yellow>中等</color>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "HVM 004"
msgid_plural "HVM 004"
msgstr[0] "HVM 004"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the HVM 004 is the fourth gun, and first shotgun, manufactured by <info>High Value Metrics (HVM)</info>. we are not sure why there isn't a third weapon in the line. \n"
"it's a <color_yellow>very weak shotgun</color> compared to it's competitors, but it's unreal use of some sort of <info>compression or nano technology</info> inside it's chamber makes this shotgun capable of holding up to <good>25 shells</good>, but takes <bad>long to reload</bad>. \n"
"this shotgun is possibly based on Beneli M4 (due to its famous semi-auto firing capability) with a gunstock grip and very squared green look.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>average</color> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"HVM 004 是 <info>高价值指标公司（HVM）</info> 制造的第四款枪械，也是第一款霰弹枪。我们不确定为何该系列没有第三款武器。\n"
"与竞争对手相比，它是一款 <color_yellow>非常弱的霰弹枪</color>，但其枪膛内运用了某种 <info>压缩或纳米技术</info>，使得这把霰弹枪能够容纳多达 <good>25 发子弹</good>，但<bad>装填时间较长</bad>。\n"
"这把霰弹枪可能基于伯奈利 M4（因其著名的半自动射击能力），带有枪托握把和非常方正、绿色的外观。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <color_yellow>中等</color>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "HVM 005 G-Class"
msgid_plural "HVM 005 G-Class"
msgstr[0] "HVM 005 G级"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the HVM 005 G-Class is an assault rifle produced by <info>High Value Metrics (HVM)</info> \n"
"it's the <bad>weakest</bad> assault rifle compared to it's competitors. \n"
"it uses the same <info>small caliber</info> ammunition as the HVM 001 and HVM 002, it's a bullpup rifle, it is inspired by the L85 or the FAMAS with a blocky design with a stylish green camo pattern.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>average</color> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"HVM 005 G级 是 <info>高价值指标公司（HVM）</info> 生产的一款突击步枪。\n"
"与竞争对手相比，它是 <bad>最弱</bad> 的突击步枪。\n"
"它使用与 HVM 001 和 HVM 002 相同的 <info>小口径</info> 弹药，是一款无托式步枪，设计灵感来自 L85 或 FAMAS，具有方正的外形和时尚的绿色迷彩涂装。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <color_yellow>中等</color>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "HVM 008"
msgid_plural "HVM 008"
msgstr[0] "HVM 008"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the HVM 008 is a low class LMG produced by <info>High Value Metrics (HVM)</info> \n"
"it's the <bad>weakest</bad> LMG compared to it's competitors. it uses the same <info>small caliber</info> ammunition as the HVM 001 and HVM 002 \n"
"the HVM 008 is possibly inspired off of the combination of the M60 (appearance) and the MG34 (using drums as feed system) with a blocky design with a stylish green camo pattern.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>average</color> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"HVM 008 是 <info>高价值指标公司（HVM）</info> 生产的一款低级别轻机枪。\n"
"与竞争对手相比，它是 <bad>最弱</bad> 的轻机枪。它使用与 HVM 001 和 HVM 002 相同的 <info>小口径</info> 弹药。\n"
"HVM 008 的设计灵感可能结合了 M60（外观）和 MG34（使用弹鼓供弹系统），具有方正的外形和时尚的绿色迷彩涂装。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <color_yellow>中等</color>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Ronson 45"
msgid_plural "Ronson 45"
msgstr[0] "朗森45型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Ronson 45 is the only pistol manufactured by <info>Ronson</info.\n"
"One of the most <good>powerful</good> commercially available hand guns. What it lacks in its relatively <bad>small clip size</bad> it makes up for in sheer stopping power\n"
"it has multiple blue panels on top of a black build.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>decent</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"朗森45型是<info>朗森</info>公司生产的唯一一款手枪。\n"
"作为市面上最<good>威力强大</good>的手枪之一，它虽然<bad>弹匣容量较小</bad>，但凭借其纯粹的停止力弥补了这一不足。\n"
"枪身以黑色为底，顶部配有多块蓝色面板。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能尚可</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Ronson 50"
msgid_plural "Ronson 50"
msgstr[0] "朗森50型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Ronson 50 is an almost <good>unreal</good> SMG produced by <info>Ronson<7info>.\n"
"Nicknamed '<info>Boneshaker</info>' the 50 is an SMG that uses the <info>LBM</info> round making for a very manouverable yet <bad>loud</bad> and <good>powerful</good> small weapon.\n"
"it has a blue panel on top of it's dark frame, it has a small grip and a base red dot sight with a rail to mount another sight, it also has a quite balanced rounded stock.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>decent</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"朗森50型是<info>朗森</info>生产的一款近乎<good>不可思议</good>的冲锋枪。\n"
"绰号“<info>骨震器</info>”的50型冲锋枪使用<info>LBM</info>弹药，使其成为一款机动性极强但<bad>噪音大</bad>且<good>威力十足</good>的小型武器。\n"
"深色枪身上方有一块蓝色面板，配有小握把、基础红点瞄准镜及可加装其他瞄具的导轨，还有一个相当平衡的圆形枪托。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能尚可</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Ronson 55"
msgid_plural "Ronson 55"
msgstr[0] "朗森55型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Ronson 55 is an almost <good>unreal</good> SMG produces by <info>Ronson</info>. it's the successor to the Ronson 50.\n"
"<good>Twin 'recoilless' alternating barrels</good> allow for accuracy and an extremely <good>high rate of fire</good>. One of the most innovative and deadly submachine guns available anywhere.\n"
"it has a blue panel on top of it's dark frame, it has a small grip and a base red dot sight with no rail to mount another sight, it also has a quite balanced rounded stock.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>decent</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"朗森55型是<info>朗森</info>生产的一款近乎<good>不可思议</good>的冲锋枪，是朗森50型的后继型号。\n"
"<good>双管“无后坐力”交替射击</good>设计确保了精准度和极高的<good>射速</good>，是现有最具创新性和致命性的冲锋枪之一。\n"
"深色枪身上方有一块蓝色面板，配有小握把和基础红点瞄准镜（无加装瞄具的导轨），还有一个相当平衡的圆形枪托。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能尚可</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Ronson 65-a"
msgid_plural "Ronson 65-a"
msgstr[0] "朗森65-a型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Ronson 65-a is an assault rifle produced by <info>Ronson</info>. it looks more like an smg but the weapon is advertised as an assault rifle, and as such the 'a' in the name can stand for 'assault'.\n"
"Most soldiers know <info>Ronson</info> for the 65-a assault rifle. Perfectly balanced stock and narrow bore combine to create a very <good>easy to use</good> and <good>accurate</good> weapon.\n"
"it has a blue panel on top of it's dark frame, it has a small grip and a base red dot sight with no rail to mount another sight, it also has a quite balanced rounded stock.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>decent</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"朗森65-a型是<info>朗森</info>生产的突击步枪。它看起来更像冲锋枪，但被宣传为突击步枪，因此名称中的“a”可代表“突击”。\n"
"大多数士兵通过65-a突击步枪认识<info>朗森</info>。完美平衡的枪托和窄口径相结合，造就了这款非常<good>易于使用</good>且<good>精准</good>的武器。\n"
"深色枪身上方有一块蓝色面板，配有小握把和基础红点瞄准镜（无加装瞄具的导轨），还有一个相当平衡的圆形枪托。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能尚可</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Ronson 70"
msgid_plural "Ronson 70"
msgstr[0] "朗森70型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Ronson 70 is an assault rifle produced by <good>Ronson</good>.\n"
"Ronson's top of the range assault rifle. Highly tuned electromechanics generate incredibly accurate and powerful <info>plasma bolts</info>.\n"
"it has a blue panel on top of it's dark frame, it has a small grip and a rail to mount a sight, it also has a quite balanced stock. the build can resemble an M16.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>decent</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"朗森70型是<good>朗森</good>生产的突击步枪。\n"
"作为朗森的顶级突击步枪，其高度调校的机电系统能产生极其精准和强大的<info>等离子弹</info>。\n"
"深色枪身上方有一块蓝色面板，配有小握把和可加装瞄具的导轨，还有一个相当平衡的枪托。外形类似M16。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能尚可</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Ronson LBM"
msgid_plural "Ronson LBM"
msgstr[0] "朗森LBM型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Ronson LBM is a heavy LMG produced by <info>Ronson</info>.\n"
"Ronson Large Bore Machine Gun. Uses <info>heavy clip</info> instead of a belt to accommodate <info>extra large rounds</info>, the LBM can devastate most targets with ease.\n"
"it has a blue panel on top of it's dark frame, it has a small grip and a rail to mount a sight, it also has a quite balanced stock. it also features an underbarrel bipod, making it <bad>impossible to mount</bad> anything under the barrel.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>decent</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"朗森LBM型是<info>朗森</info>生产的重型轻机枪。\n"
"朗森大口径机枪。使用<info>重型弹匣</info>而非弹链来容纳<info>超大号弹药</info>，LBM型能轻松摧毁大多数目标。\n"
"深色枪身上方有一块蓝色面板，配有小握把和可加装瞄具的导轨，还有一个相当平衡的枪托。它还配备了下挂式两脚架，使得枪管下方<bad>无法加装</bad>任何配件。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能尚可</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 313"
msgid_plural "RIA 313"
msgstr[0] "RIA 313型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the RIA 313 is one of the first pistols designed by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"it's a very light pistol and uses a <info>small caliber</info> ammunition type \n"
"the weapon looks like a futuristic pistol that appears to be a combination of the M9 or SIG-Sauer P226 for its look and the Desert Eagle for its size, a large muzzle and a pair of re-designed sights, the weapon has a sleek dark gray and black metallic look to it.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 313型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>设计的第一批手枪之一。\n"
"这是一款非常轻巧的手枪，使用<info>小口径</info>弹药。\n"
"武器外观类似未来风格手枪，似乎是M9或SIG-Sauer P226的外观与沙漠之鹰尺寸的结合体，拥有大型枪口和一对重新设计的瞄具，整体呈现光滑的深灰色和黑色金属质感。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 1010"
msgid_plural "RIA 1010"
msgstr[0] "RIA 1010型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the RIA 1010 is one of the last pistols designed by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> before the cataclysm \n"
"it's a very light pistol and uses a <info>medium ammunition</info> type \n"
"the weapon looks like a possible variant of the RIA 313 with a slightly smaller size, a larger clip, a compensator and a unique grip/flashlight on the bottom, the weapon has a sleek dark gray and black metallic look to it.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 1010型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>在灾变前设计的最后一批手枪之一。\n"
"这是一款非常轻巧的手枪，使用<info>中型弹药</info>。\n"
"武器外观可能是RIA 313型的变体，尺寸略小，弹匣更大，配有补偿器和底部独特的握把/手电筒，整体呈现光滑的深灰色和黑色金属质感。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 7"
msgid_plural "RIA 7"
msgstr[0] "RIA 7型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the RIA 7 is a <good>lightweight</good> smg developed by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"it's a very light smg and uses <info>five-seven's 5.7mm</info> ammunition \n"
"the weapon is a futuristic submachine gun which is similar to the MP5 due to its look. It has a short barrel, a slightly large magazine and a short buttstock, the weapon has a sleek dark gray and black metallic look to it.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 7型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>开发的<good>轻量化</good>冲锋枪。\n"
"这是一款非常轻巧的冲锋枪，使用<info>五七式5.7毫米</info>弹药。\n"
"武器外观类似MP5的未来风格冲锋枪，拥有短枪管、稍大的弹匣和短枪托，整体呈现光滑的深灰色和黑色金属质感。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA T7"
msgid_plural "RIA T7"
msgstr[0] "RIA T7型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the RIA T7 is a lightweight smg developed by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"it's a very light smg upgraded from it's brother, the RIA 7, and uses <info>five-seven's 5.7mm</info> ammunition\n"
" the weapon is a futuristic submachine gun which is similar to the MP5 due to its look. It has a short barrel, a slightly large magazine and a short buttstock, the weapon has a sleek dark gray and black metallic look to it.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA T7型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>开发的轻量化冲锋枪。\n"
"这是从其兄弟型号RIA 7型升级而来的非常轻巧的冲锋枪，使用<info>五七式5.7毫米</info>弹药。\n"
"武器外观类似MP5的未来风格冲锋枪，拥有短枪管、稍大的弹匣和短枪托，整体呈现光滑的深灰色和黑色金属质感。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 20 Para"
msgid_plural "RIA 20 Para"
msgstr[0] "RIA 20伞兵型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA 20 Para is a light assault rifle produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA 20 Para is a futuristic rifle with the size of an SMG \n"
"This makes it quite similar to the AKS-74U (an assault rifle that is popular and famous for its high power and small size), which is a variant of the AK-74, which replaces the AKM, a modified version of the latter. It has a telescopic sight and possible sling mounts.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 20伞兵型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>生产的轻型突击步枪。\n"
"RIA 20伞兵型是一款未来风格步枪，尺寸与冲锋枪相当。\n"
"这使得它非常类似于AKS-74U（一款以高威力和小尺寸而闻名流行的突击步枪），后者是AK-74的变体，取代了经过改良的AKM。它配备有伸缩式瞄准镜和可能的背带挂点。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 20 DSC"
msgid_plural "RIA 20 DSC"
msgstr[0] "RIA 20 DSC型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA 20 DSC is a light assault rifle produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA 20 DSC is a futuristic rifle, it's a bulkier & longer version of the RIA 20 Para. It has a different buttstock, barrel, telescopic sight, a quite unique magazine and a short muzzle.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 20 DSC型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>生产的轻型突击步枪。\n"
"RIA 20 DSC型是一款未来风格步枪，是RIA 20伞兵型更庞大、更长的版本。它拥有不同的枪托、枪管、伸缩式瞄准镜、相当独特的弹匣和短枪口。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 20 Striker"
msgid_plural "RIA 20 Striker"
msgstr[0] "RIA 20打击者型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA 20 Striker is a light assault rifle produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA 20 Striker uses the same structure of the RIA 20 DSC with a longer muzzle, the same telescopic sight of the Para model, a more realistic magazine design. It also has a red glowing line on its body.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>average</color> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 20打击者型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>生产的轻型突击步枪。\n"
"RIA 20打击者型采用与RIA 20 DSC型相同的结构，但枪口更长，配备与伞兵型号相同的伸缩式瞄准镜和更真实的弹匣设计。枪身上还有一条红色发光线条。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<color_yellow>性能一般</color>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA Trident"
msgid_plural "RIA Trident"
msgstr[0] "RIA三叉戟型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA Trident is a heavy assault rifle produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA Trident is a futuristic rifle with its body based off of the M249, which is a LMG. It has a realistic buttstock, a rear sight and a visible ejection port, but with no bolt handle. It also has <good>three barrels</info>, each coloured differently to signify its damage type.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA三叉戟型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>生产的重型突击步枪。\n"
"RIA三叉戟型是一款未来风格步枪，其枪身基于M249轻机枪。它拥有真实的枪托、后瞄准镜和可见的抛壳口，但没有拉机柄。它还拥有<good>三根枪管</good>，每根颜色不同以标示其伤害类型。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 30 Strikeforce"
msgid_plural "RIA 30 Strikeforce"
msgstr[0] "RIA 30打击力量型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the RIA 30 Strikeforce is the only shotgun manufactured by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA 30 Strikeforce's design is similar to a sawn-off Ithaca 37 shotgun in terms of appearance. It has no front and rear sight and has a handguard that appears to be a shotgun pump on first glance.\n"
" which is not.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 30打击力量型是<info>卢比孔工业</info>制造的唯一一款霰弹枪。\n"
"RIA 30打击力量型的设计在外观上类似于截短版的伊萨卡37型霰弹枪。它没有前后瞄准镜，护木乍看之下像是霰弹枪的泵动装置，但实际上并非如此。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能良好</good>，<good>不易发生故障</good>，且<good>相当耐操</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 40"
msgid_plural "RIA 40"
msgstr[0] "RIA 40"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA 40 is a LMG produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA 40 looks similar to the GPMG M240 with a telescopic sight, the RIA 40 has a <color_yellow>smaller magazine</color> compared to the other LMGs, but it packs a harder punch.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 40 是 <info>Rubicon 工业公司</info> 生产的一款轻机枪。\n"
"RIA 40 外观类似 GPMG M240，配有伸缩式瞄准镜。与其他轻机枪相比，RIA 40 的 <color_yellow>弹匣容量较小</color>，但威力更强。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <good>良好</good>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA T40"
msgid_plural "RIA T40"
msgstr[0] "RIA T40"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA 40 is the second LMG produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"The RIA T40 is simply a slightly re-designed version of RIA 40. In addition, it has some glowing red lines, the RIA T40 has a <color_yellow>smaller magazine</color> compared to the other LMGs, but it packs an even harder punch.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA T40 是 <info>Rubicon 工业公司</info> 生产的第二款轻机枪。\n"
"RIA T40 是 RIA 40 的略微重新设计版本。此外，它带有一些发光的红色线条。与其他轻机枪相比，RIA T40 的 <color_yellow>弹匣容量较小</color>，但威力更强。\n"
"\n"
"此武器性能 <good>良好</good>，<good>可能不易发生故障</good>且<good>相当耐用。</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno 的 SAS4 武器包模组内容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "RIA 45"
msgid_plural "RIA 45"
msgstr[0] "RIA 45"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The RIA 45 is a LMG produced by <info>Rubicon Industries</info> \n"
"it's an attempt to produce a <good>lighter</good> version of the RIA40. the RIA 45 Para is modeled after its linemate, the RIA 40. It has a telescopic sight as well. The only things that makes it different from the RIA 45 is a hollow buttstock and a shorter barrel.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"RIA 45 是 <info>Rubicon 工业公司</info> 生产的一款轻机枪。\n"
